Template: percona-xtradb-cluster-server/error_setting_password
Type: error
Description: Unable to set password for the Percona XtraDB Cluster "root" user
 An error occurred while setting the password for the Percona XtraDB Cluster
 administrative user. This may have happened because the account
 already has a password, or because of a communication problem with
 the Percona Server daemon.
 .
 You should check the account's password after the package installation.
 .
 Please read the /usr/share/doc/percona-xtradb-cluster-server-5.7/README.Debian file
 for more information.

Template: percona-xtradb-cluster-server/password_mismatch
Type: error
Description: Password input error
 The two passwords you entered were not the same. Please try again.

Template: percona-xtradb-cluster-server/no_upgrade_when_using_ndb
Type: error
Description: NDB Cluster seems to be in use
 percona-xtradb-cluster-5.7 has orphaned NDB Cluster support. Please migrate to the
 new mysql-cluster package and remove all lines starting with "ndb" from
 all config files below /etc/mysql/.
